# session-types

Importance Score: 45/100

The platform implements three distinct psychic reading session formats:

## Session Categories
Location: /index.html

1. Text Chat
- Asynchronous text-based communication format
- Implied separate billing model
- Default entry-level session type

2. Voice Call
- Audio-only consultation format
- Minute-by-minute billing structure

3. Video Session
- Full video consultation capability
- Premium session format
- Includes viewer count display for active streams
- Time-to-start indicators for scheduled sessions

## Status Integration
The session types interface with the reader availability system:
- Online: Available for new sessions
- Busy: Currently in an active session
- Away: Temporarily unavailable for sessions

## UI Implementation
- Each session type displays distinct pricing models
- Stream status indicators for video sessions
- Real-time availability indicators per session type
- Viewer count metrics for active video streams

